{"tid":352547,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【759阿信屋】759茶餐廳就快絕種！雲吞麵得返一間","createTime":"2017-08-09T00:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T06:09:35.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fccdfec6868f39653dba4ce7be86dbb3fe48f36","tid":352547,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502190871_dde5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502190871_dde5.jpg&h=c3c0658f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502190973_940a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502190973_940a.jpg&h=f9f0e442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n759飯堂已結業(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n759阿信屋始2014年發展多品牌路線，不過今年初起便陸續削減副線，部分壽命僅得3年。據759官網顯示，開業僅一年的759飯堂已於今年結業，其餘飲食業務包括雲吞麵及車仔麵亦於今年上半年各關閉一間。林偉駿透露，未來2至3個月因租約期滿會再關閉唯一位於葵涌區的759茶餐廳，「條數平平，無謂做！」<br />\n<br />\n本報近日到759各副線視察，其茶餐廳、雲吞麵及車仔麵於午飯時間有10多位顧客，一客午餐價錢約30至40港元。不過非食肆如主打家電的「759Kaguya」面積雖然大，但店內貨品與一般阿信屋無異，只得數十款電器品牌，其餘則以零食為主，店內亦有不少貨箱堆在走廊，釀成不便。<br />\n<br />\n集團高峰時曾多達14個品牌，惟根據官方網站，現時759只尚餘10個品牌，當中Kaguya、雲吞麵、茶餐廳亦只得一間，車仔麵、Skyland及麵包工房亦各得3間。林偉駿直言，事實上「間間都係差唔多嘢，純粹等業主唔好覺得下下叫阿信屋」，目的是當初想搶佔市場份額以提高議價能力。但他強調，現時旗下飲食業務做得不錯，未有再削減食肆打算，副線分店數目會維持現狀。<br />\n<br />\n記者:范穎琛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57057270&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57057270%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170809&d=hiO3DfHFJ8tI%2BuOtwDxSdv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=7c9b74b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57057270%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170809&h=7ee29227\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57057270&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170809</a>"},{"pid":"b9b3b2387e78b7fb96579dd7f4fbdf78024cfdce","tid":352547,"uid":72908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:26:14.000Z","msg":"敗在亂鳩擴充業務 <br />\n唔專注做本行"},{"pid":"0b74f52c83d95cdb52a44b95a7cbd8c46d0ed567","tid":352547,"uid":29851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"個品牌柒到仆街睇見都唔想入去幫襯，條友仲以為自己真係好勁好有號召力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af795d333b1bcf78f778026c250864510bbb28e","tid":352547,"uid":39527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"抵死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f7044718ad77806363151b6acd49d3ecc4fc25","tid":352547,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"759茶餐廳幾抵食<br />\n執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}